          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2021-10-26 20:39:46" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>(derivative of {L:ἔδαφος&lt;SDBG:ἔδαφος:000000&gt;} ‘ground,’ {D:1.44}) to destroy or tear down, by causing something to be brought down to the level of the ground</DefinitionShort>
